Company description: At Comet, we believe that, from now on, we will go to the office by intent and not by obligation.  We want the office to be like a hotel, enhanced with services we do not have at our disposal at home. With the working world subject to far-reaching reforms, face-to-face moments between colleagues will become increasingly anchored around collaboration and conviviality, in suitable venues.  Comet is an expert in venues where the collective is (re)created. We do so through two activities: Comet Meetings, a network of next-generation venues dedicated to strategic meetings (teambuilding, seminars, Excoms, afterwork), located in the heart of Paris, Brussels and Madrid. Designed to facilitate team collaboration and creativity, these locations offer unique and inspiring settings, high-end services (catering, wellness, successful meetings expertise) at all-inclusive prices that are accessible to everyone. Hospitality by Comet, a range of office services that transforms workplaces into actual living spaces, in order to facilitate employees‚Äô daily lives and meet the challenges of new ways of working. With Hospitality, we propose a range of flexible spaces (coworking, ultra-equipped next-gen meeting rooms) to real estate owners, as well as a wide portfolio of hotel-inspired services (community management, wellness, concierge services, reception, etc.), to meet the need for flexibility vs. the traditional 3/6/9 lease contracts. Discover the Comet experience and our solutions on www.comet-meetings.com
